css_variables.example:
```css
:root {
  /* Primary Palette */
  --color-mystical-purple: #6B4E8B;
  --color-twilight-deep: #4A3560;
  --color-twilight-light: #9B7EBD;
  --color-autumn-gold: #D4A046;
  --color-autumn-amber: #C87D2F;
  --color-harvest-light: #E8C589;
  --color-forest-green: #4A7856;
  --color-moss-deep: #344A3D;
  --color-sage-light: #9FB8A7;
  --color-earth-brown: #7A5C4D;
  --color-bark-deep: #4D3A2F;
  --color-sand-light: #E8DDD0;

  /* Semantic Mappings */
  --color-conscious: var(--color-autumn-gold);
  --color-unconscious: var(--color-mystical-purple);
  --color-defined: var(--color-forest-green);
  --color-undefined-light: var(--color-sage-light);
  --color-active-channel: var(--color-autumn-amber);

  /* Functional Colors - Light Mode */
  --bg-primary: #F5F1EB;
  --bg-secondary: var(--color-sand-light);
  --text-primary: var(--color-bark-deep);
  --text-secondary: var(--color-earth-brown);
  --border-default: #B8A695;
}

[data-theme="dark"] {
  --bg-primary: #1C1410;
  --bg-secondary: #2A211D;
  --text-primary: var(--color-sand-light);
  --text-secondary: #C4B5A6;
  --border-default: var(--color-bark-deep);
}
```

human_design_center.example:
```css
.hd-center {
  border: 2px solid var(--color-earth-brown);
  transition: all 0.2s ease;
}

.hd-center--defined {
  background-color: var(--color-forest-green);
  opacity: 1;
}

.hd-center--undefined {
  background-color: var(--color-sage-light);
  opacity: 0.6;
}

.hd-center:hover {
  transform: scale(1.05);
  filter: brightness(1.1);
}

.hd-center--selected {
  border: 3px solid var(--color-autumn-gold);
  box-shadow: 0 0 12px rgba(212, 160, 70, 0.4);
}
```

gate_activation.example:
```css
.gate-activation {
  width: 12px;
  height: 12px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  border: 2px solid var(--color-earth-brown);
}

.gate-activation--conscious {
  background-color: var(--color-autumn-gold);
  box-shadow: 0 0 6px rgba(212, 160, 70, 0.5);
}

.gate-activation--unconscious {
  background-color: var(--color-mystical-purple);
  box-shadow: 0 0 6px rgba(107, 78, 139, 0.5);
}

.gate-activation:focus-visible {
  outline: 3px solid var(--color-autumn-gold);
  outline-offset: 2px;
}
```

interaction_chart.example:
```css
.chart-person-a {
  --person-color: var(--color-autumn-gold);
  --person-label-bg: var(--color-harvest-light);
}

.chart-person-b {
  --person-color: var(--color-mystical-purple);
  --person-label-bg: var(--color-twilight-light);
}

.chart-composite {
  --composite-color: var(--color-forest-green);
  mix-blend-mode: multiply;
  opacity: 0.8;
}

.electromagnetic-connection {
  stroke: var(--color-autumn-amber);
  stroke-width: 3px;
  animation: pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
}

@keyframes pulse {
  0%, 100% { opacity: 0.8; }
  50% { opacity: 1; }
}
```
